&lt;p&gt;Conclusion I: Some boats are steamers. &amp;rarr; False (It is not definite)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Conclusion II: No ships are boats. &amp;rarr; True (It is definite)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Conclusion III: Some steamers are ships. &amp;rarr; True (It is definite)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, only conclusions II and III follow.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;न्यूनतम संभव वेन आरेख है:&lt;/p&gt;

